 [[Rhino Records|Rhino]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 2004\n|''[[Days of Darkness (album)|Days of Darkness]]''\n*Released: 2004\n*Label: Spitfire\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 2007\n|''[[The Spitfire Collection]]''\n*Released: 2007\n*Label: Spitfire\n|}\n\n==EP albums==\n{| class =\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album details\n! colspan=\"1\"| Peak chart positions\n|-\n!style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"|[[MegaCharts|NLD]]<br /><ref name=\"NLD\"/>\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1987\n|''[[Live at Eindhoven]]''\n*Released: 1987\n*Label: Atlantic/Megaforce\n|align=\"center\"| 62\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1993\n|''[[Return to the Apocalyptic City]]''\n*Released: 1993\n*Label: Atlantic/Megaforce\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"15\" style=\"font-size: 8pt\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a release that did not chart.\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:4em;\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Song\n! colspan=\"1\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"| [[Hot Mainstream Rock Tracks|US<br />Main.]]<br /><ref name=\"US\" />\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1987\n| \"Over the Wall\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| ''The Legacy''\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1988\n| \"Trial by Fire\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| ''The New Order''\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 1989\n| \"[[Practice What You Preach (Testament song)|Practice What You Preach]]\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Practice What You Preach''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"3\"| 1990\n| \"Greenhouse Effect\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| \"Souls of Black\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Souls of Black''\n|-\n| \"The Legacy\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"| 1992\n| \"Electric Crown\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''The Ritual''\n|-\n| \"Return to Serenity\"\n| align=\"center\"| 22\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"| 1994\n| \"Low\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''Low''\n|-\n| \"Dog Faced Gods\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"| 2012\n| \"True American Hate\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Dark Roots of Earth''\n|-\n| \"Native Blood\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 2016\n| \"The Pale King\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| ''Brotherhood of the Snake''\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 2020\n| \"Night of the Witch\"\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| ''Titans of Creation''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 8pt\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a release that did not chart.\n|}\n\n== Music Videos==\n*''Over the Wall'' (1987)\n*''Trial By Fire'' (1988)\n*''Nobody's Fault'' (1988)\n*''Practice What You Preach'' (1989)\n*''Greenhouse Effect'' (1990)\n*''The Ballad'' (1990)\n*''Souls of Black'' (1990)\n*''The Legacy'' (1990)\n*''Electric Crown'' (1992)\n*''Return to Serenity'' (1992)\n*''Low'' (1994)\n*''More Than Meets The Eye'' (2008)\n*''Native Blood'' (2012)\n*''The Pale King'' (2016)\n*''Night Of The Witch (Lyric Video)'' (2020)\n\n== Videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Video details\n! colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart positions\n|-\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"| SWE<br /><ref>http://www.sverigetopplistan.se</ref>\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"| SWI<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitparade.ch/charts/musik-dvd/03-11-2013 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-08-17 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813201320/http://hitparade.ch/charts/musik-dvd/03-11-2013 |archivedate=2014-08-13 }}</ref>\n|-\n| 1991\n| '''''[[Seen Between the Lines]]'''''\n* Released: June 25, 1991\n* Label: Atlantic\n* Format: [[VHS]]\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|-\n| 2005\n| '''''[[Live in London (Testament album)|Live in London]]'''''\n* Released: November 1, 2005\n* Label: Spitfire\n* Format: [[DVD]]\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| 